            Michael Cohen: What Trump lashing out at his ex-lawyer reveals
            Michael Cohen is a liar and a "weak person", according to the president, who lashed out at his ex-lawyer after he pleaded guilty to lying to Congress. The BBC's Anthony Zurcher analyses Mr Trump's response.This video has been optimised for mobile viewing on the BBC News app. The BBC News app is available from the Apple App Store for iPhone and Google Play Store for Android.
                
